8.3 Dialogs (14)
------------------

  Dialog                  File                             Description
  ──────                  ────                             ───────────
  PatientDialog           ui/shared/patient_dialogs.py     Add/Edit patient with
                                                           conditions checklist
  PatientProfileDialog    ui/shared/patient_dialogs.py     Read-only 4-tab profile
