  EmployeeDialog          ui/shared/employee_dialogs.py    Add/Edit employee
  EmployeeProfileDialog   ui/shared/employee_dialogs.py    Read-only 3-tab profile
  HREmployeeDialog        ui/shared/hr_employee_dialogs.py Extends EmployeeDialog
                                                           with salary + emergency
  HREmployeeProfileDialog ui/shared/hr_employee_dialogs.py Enhanced 4-tab profile
                                                           with Salary & HR tab
  UserAccountDialog       ui/shared/hr_employee_dialogs.py Create user account
  AppointmentDialog       ui/shared/appointment_dialog.py  Full appointment form
                                                           with recurring support
  QueueEditDialog         ui/shared/clinical_dialogs.py    Edit queue entry
  ServiceEditDialog       ui/shared/clinical_dialogs.py    Add/Edit service
  NewInvoiceDialog        ui/shared/clinical_dialogs.py    Multi-item invoice with
                                                           auto-discount
  PaymentDialog           ui/shared/clinical_dialogs.py    Payment with change
                                                           calculation
  BulkPriceDialog         ui/shared/clinical_dialogs.py    Batch service price
                                                           update

8.4 Chart Widgets (3)
----------------------

  BarChartWidget    Horizontal bar chart via QPainter
  PieChartWidget    Pie/donut chart via QPainter.drawPie()
  HBarChartWidget   Horizontal bar with per-bar color support

All charts are custom-painted — no external charting library.

