  make_table_btn()      Teal action button for tables
  make_table_btn_danger() Red danger button for tables
  style_dialog_btns()   Styles Save/Cancel buttons
  make_action_cell()    Centered button cell widget


9. SECURITY & AUDIT FEATURES
==============================

  - Password hashing on user creation
  - Forced password change on first login (must_change_password flag)
  - Role-based access control — sidebar pages, button visibility, data
    filtering all enforced per role
  - Full activity log — every Create, Update, Delete, Login, and Leave
    action is recorded with timestamp, user email, and detail
  - Cascading deletes — deleting a patient or employee safely removes all
    related records (conditions, appointments, queue entries, invoices,
    invoice items)
  - Conflict detection — appointment scheduling checks for double-booked
    doctors
  - Input validation — phone numbers (+63 prefix, 10 digits), email regex,
    date range enforcement, duplicate phone checks


10. AUTO-REFRESH & REAL-TIME FEATURES
=======================================

  Feature                   Interval     Location
  ───────                   ────────     ────────
  Dashboard data refresh    10 seconds   DashboardPage
  Appointment list refresh  10 seconds   AppointmentsPage
  Clinical/Queue refresh    10 seconds   ClinicalPage
  Analytics refresh         15 seconds   AnalyticsPage
  Notification polling      15 seconds   MainWindow (non-Admin/HR)
  Leave auto-expiry         5 minutes    MainWindow
  Activity log smart-refresh On switch   ActivityLogPage (only if new entries)
  Clock display             1 second     DashboardPage


