12. SUMMARY
=============

Go-onCARE is a complete clinic management desktop application featuring:

  - 17 database tables with 8 pre-built views and 16 indexes
  - 5 distinct user roles with granular access control
  - 100+ backend API methods across 9 specialized mixins
  - 10 page-level widgets and 14 dialog classes
  - 3 custom-painted chart widgets (no external dependencies)
  - Full audit trail logging every system action
  - Real-time auto-refresh across all views (10-15 second intervals)
  - Automated leave management with expiry and notifications
  - Multi-item invoicing with auto-discount and partial payments
  - Recurring appointment scheduling with conflict detection
  - Patient merge capability for deduplication
  - Cascading deletes that maintain referential integrity

All built with Python 3, PyQt6, and MySQL — zero external UI/chart libraries.
